{"tid":1918420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《世界要記住血的教訓 》 武漢肺炎減退之後一定要有場世界性既反中遊行","createTime":"2020-03-10T05:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T10:03:37.000Z","uid":13138,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ea8f0592e28fb08e300ca985be578e64313c87a2","tid":1918420,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:51:49.000Z","msg":"好似前幾年，港豬根本唔明點解啲人要反共，到真係燒到埋身先識驚。其他國家一樣，覺得中國冇人權冇自由唔關佢地事，識賺人仔就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但正正因為中國冇自由冇人權，最後肺炎傳到全世界都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>政府上下隱瞞消息，冇人監督到，外交部又周圍同人講：没事儿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲人衛生水平差，冇文明冇公德心，去其他國家播毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共唔人道隔離啲人，嚇到佢地周圍走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n滲透曬應該持平既國際組織，呃鳩其他國家話冇事，日日吹捧中國處理得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球開始爆發，大陸扣起曬外資工廠啲口罩消毒用品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肺炎完咗一定要有場世界性反中遊行，記住依個血的教訓，話比全世界知中國既唔文明冇自由亦唔係事不關己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隨時影響你身家性命財產<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順便可以悼念埋全世界比邪惡中共肺炎害死既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩光環都有齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279c846604ec200a96d4e019eea7fbf37270f44e","tid":1918420,"uid":19667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:53:55.000Z","msg":"樓主講得好"},{"pid":"3a0f6ea17c90cb44ace737a17f77791a1eceb9f7","tid":1918420,"uid":131282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:55:29.000Z","msg":"係 臨選舉冇人血饅頭點血債票償？"},{"pid":"e4f1e1a0bb01dccf4ff4833f0adbc8307b4df880","tid":1918420,"uid":13138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim